cdata.name: Imbrex
cdata.desc: Imbrex is a blockchain-based listing platform for the real-estate industry where users control their own data, have faster transaction times and be incentivised for participation.REX aimsto connect vendors, buyers and agents over aopen network.REX is an Ethereum-based token that will be used within the platform to pay vendors and agent. REX can also be exchanged within the platform for features like professional profile creation and profile promotion.
